snippet.title: Level Iterations | Artifice: War Tactics (Alpha)
snippet.description:
Artifice: War tactics is a turn-based strategy game all about setting up tripwires and executing killer combos. 

We have come a long way since the inception of "Artifice: War Tactics". A Throwback video showing iterations of our Hunari level. The quest continues... 

Don't forget to follow us on Twitter, Instagram and Discord.

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/silvinegamestudios/
Discord: https://discord.gg/CJAcgD4zaJ
Twitter: https://twitter.com/SilvineGame/
